@Node "INT" "Introduction"

@{b}@{u}Introduction@{uu}@{ub}

TotalCalc is a powerful calculator having the following main features:

   - Possibility to exchange among different numeration systems: floating
     point, decimal integer, hexadecimal, binary.
   - Up to 13 normal digits plus 2 digits for the exponent of ten (scientific
     notation).
   - Arithmetical operations.
   - Powers, roots, logarithms, reciprocal, factorial, trigonometric
     functions, percent functions.
   - Logical operations.
   - Up to 20 nested parentheses.
   - Up to 10 independent memories.
   - Constant calculus.

Moreover, it is a standard commodity, it supports the Amiga clipboard, and it
uses any font of your choice.


@Endnode
@Node "SYR" "System requirements"

@{b}@{u}System requirements@{uu}@{ub}

TotalCalc requires Kickstart 2.04+ and the following libraries in the LIBS:
directory:

   - diskfont.library
   - mathieeedoubbas.library
   - mathieeedoubtrans.library


@Endnode
@Node "INS" "Installation"

@{b}@{u}Installation@{uu}@{ub}

To install TotalCalc, simply drag its icon to any drawer of your choice.


@Endnode
